ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Classic 19th century Russian lit course with an Art twist...
Definitely would recommend this course to others. Teaches a great deal about both literary and visual Realism in Russia which is useful for students in Slavic and outside of it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Gave me a better appreciation of Realism, the most dominant aesthetic mode in 19th cent. Russia and as a result I am better prepared to discuss it for both exams and as I prepare dissertation ideas.
